meta.name: Arginine Dipeptide
meta.description:
This map was generated using KPCovR with
Î±=0.55 and 2 principal components, using conformer energy as the biaising
property and SOAP structural descriptors.

The structures of 2109 bare arginine dipeptides were taken from the Berlin
amino acid database.
references: *Structure-Property Maps with Kernel Principal Covariates Regression* B. A. Helfrecht, R. K. Cersonsky, G. Fraux, M. Ceriotti, https://arxiv.org/abs/2002.05076

*First-principles data set of 45,892 isolated and cation-coordinated conformers of 20 proteinogenic amino acids*, M. Ropo, M. Schneider, C. Baldauf, V. Blum, Scientific Data 3, 160009 (2016), https://doi.org/10.1038/sdata.2016.9
